name: Charlie "GTA" Thompson
Location: New York City, United States, Earth
bio: I don't care what you guys say. I'm the king. I'm literally a CEO. I've already played GTA 6. And I know what you're thinking - it hasn't even come out stupid kid. Well I'm telling you that's just how next level I am. I literally made the game. Yes, that's right. I created GTA 6. All those memes you see about GTA 6 don't apply to me - I have the game in front of my very eyes. Now come work with me - I have single handedly created GTA.
